name: Murakami Lucky Cat Coin Bank Feeding Game Winners

metadata.description:
bleff.eth impressively won first place in the Murakami's Cat Coin Bank Game held between December 17, 2022 and January 4, 2023.
Congratulations! You did so well on Discord Chat as well. You kept the top spots throughout the game and was dubbed the "King Cat"! You mentioned how you aimed for first place because of Discord Chat and the support you received there. And you were indeed crowned the winner! Another round of applause for the limelight you deserve! You are the King Cat!
